do-fractal cell-complexes formed by polygons\nof different number of sides $m$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 May 2020 17:37:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2020 16:59:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-15"}
