ity of the Q/U domain over E/B for determination of\nthe statistical properties of the derived CMB signals, due to non-locality of\nthe transition Q/U $\\rightarrow$ E/B.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 May 2020 23:15:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-17"}
