gly regular Cayley graphs. Thus,\nwe obtain many strongly regular graphs with new parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 00:26:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 May 2020 04:02:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 May 2020 01:56:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-01"}
