R images in TextZoom. For example, it outperforms\nLapSRN by over 5% and 8%on the recognition accuracy of ASTER and CRNN. Our\nresults suggest that low-resolution text recognition in the wild is far from\nbeing solved, thus more research effort is needed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 09:18:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Jul 2020 05:42:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 2 Aug 2020 03:27:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-04"}
