immings have the potential to provide early estimates of mass and\nspeed of Earth-directed CMEs, relevant for space weather forecasts, for\nsatellite locations both at L1 and L5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 09:24:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 May 2020 16:03:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-11"}
