utgoing radiation as\nseen by a distant observer and the ingoing by a local observer in a one-to-one\nway. The two observers will use a different conformal gauge. A possible\nconnection is made with the antipodal identification and unitarity issues.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 12:25:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 21:29:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 20:30:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 19:09:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-02"}
