itive for the present example, the balance should be different for more\ncomplex systems, in particular for electrolyte solutions for the responses to\npressure, salt concentration and electric potential gradients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 13:06:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 10:03:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
