 reinforces the opinion that magnetars do not necessarily result\nfrom very energetic supernova explosions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 14:28:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2020 15:43:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-23"}
